@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ztgyno(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.17 * tmp + 0.19)) - v1)
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.05) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.04)) + (0.12 - wp.abs(v0 + 0.30)))
    v1 = 0.49
    tmp = v2
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.64) / wp.abs(v2 + 0.91)) * ((v0 + 0.10 + tmp + 0.69) - (tmp + 0.80 * v1 + 0.72)))
    v0 = wp.sin((tmp + tmp))
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.96) * (tmp + 0.90 * tmp + 0.66)) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
